(1, 'Form', 'Confidential Information', ',Topic (Sub Tab),Section #,Section Heading,Sub Section #,Sub Section Heading', '10', '30', '10', 'pdf-logo.png', '&lt;p&gt;Employees may not disclose to any outside person confidential information about Company activities, except when properly authorized to do so in the normal course of business. Similarly, employees must respect confidentiality of information received from co-workers.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;It is unethical for employees to use confidential information gained by virtue of their employment at the Company for their personal gain, or to the benefit of friends, relatives or associates.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Employees may not, either directly or indirectly, acquire or dispose of any information obtained in the course of work at the Company which has not been publically disclosed. If an employee is not sure whether or not information has been publically disclosed, they must consult with a manager or owner.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Confidential Information includes:&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Financial information&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;New products and services that are being researched and developed&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Business plans or negotiations&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Sales results&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Confidential information of all existing and future customers&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Confidential information of all co-workers&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
